  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>General</Type>
    <Text>The Comfort Inn and Suites Kings Cross is centrally located in Bloomsbury area, just 5min walk from Kings Cross tube and train station and Eurostars St Pancras station. There are several attractions within easy walking distance from the hotel, including the British Museum and Regents Park. All other attractions are easy to reach by the excellent public transport links nearby. All rooms at the hotel have en-suite bathroom with shower, air conditioning, microwave, fridge, coffee/tea making facilities, desk, in-room safe, remote control TV with satellite channels and hairdryer.  Wireless internet is available in bedrooms and open areas. Continental buffet breakfast is served from 7.00 to 09.30 on weekdays and from 07.30 to 10.00 on weekends.</Text>
